Exercise#1 Question#1

Use Cases:
Verify user can access notes with valid credentials
Verify user can't access notes with invalid credentials
Verify user can access notes in mobile(ipad, windows, mac etc.) device separately
Verify user can access notes in mobile(ipad, windows, mac etc.) device simultaneously
Verify document sharing feature between users should not exist
Verify user should only have access to his/her notes
Verify modified/deleted notes is synced across devices


Exercise#1 Question#2
First I would do Smoke/Sanity testing by logging in with valid credentials and perform exploratory/ad-hoc testing to make sure that 
app is testable before executing functional and end2end test cases
